										<li>Headlamp with spare batteries</li>
										<li>Basic first aid supplies (plasters, antiseptic)</li>
										<li>Mobile phone in waterproof case</li>
									</ul>
								</div>

								<div class="gear-category">
									<h5>Hydration & Nutrition</h5>
